cisc275.group3.scene

Class SceneTutorial

  • java.lang.Object
    • cisc275.group3.scene.Scene
      • cisc275.group3.scene.SceneTutorial
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConstructCrab, ConstructFish, ConstructHeron

    public class SceneTutorial
extends Scene
implements ConstructCrab, ConstructFish, ConstructHeron
    SceneTutorial.java is a special instance of Scene.java

    The purpose of this class is to provide the model for a functional tutorial. There are elements of the Bay, Beach and Wetland scenes.

    See Scene.java, SceneBay.java, SceneBeach.java, SceneWetland.java

    Author:
    Scott
